{"tid":1031823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請進：好後悔","createTime":"2019-02-22T02:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T02:44:47.000Z","uid":169214,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d051546fcc0ef189e226dde799c014d21e87991","tid":1031823,"uid":169214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:14:26.000Z","msg":"小弟ive仔，就畢業。返 intern 知道返工辛苦，所以好想讀大學或個 Degree，不過依個想法太遲，GPA都不過2，就算畢左業可能打份皮幾兩皮嘅工，可能咁就一世，感到絕望同後悔，我唔想停留喺依度，不過現實歸現實，都唔知未來係點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以指點下我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有得救呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2066ff21ddc7a3396914a9f427a53eab054faa8","tid":1031823,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"讀完大學又會點? 只會起步再遲四年"},{"pid":"74c7a24eea4d7e23fe239423a129525203c9adb1","tid":1031823,"uid":1834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:25:21.000Z","msg":"逃避返工所以讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"5036f52ab3d366309b172c9ee5a4f8a0b3022417","tid":1031823,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"唔過2就聽日準時返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3776a3d4660be5434b09d0d0f389991eb94298fd","tid":1031823,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"先做野，再諗，你都知自己宜家自己GPA低，仲想讀？就算比你讀到大學，考試肥晒仲閉，到時棧搞，比左學費又想quit，嘥錢嘥時間嘥心機<br />\n<br />\n不如做野先，到時你覺我你真係唔讀唔得既或工作需要既再讀返書，如果做左野之後，你覺得做野好呀，又有錢收，又學到野，又草到錢，又唔洗溫書，唔洗考試<br />\n<br />\n就算你第時做左野之後又想讀返書，都無問題呀，你都自己搵到一畢錢讀，唔洗宜家咁又伸大手問人拎，我唔知你可能問學資處借錢定唔洗比，但我覺得做左野先好d，因為你自己都唔知想點"},{"pid":"558c22271e86d541b9a0c268a321f0d471ba7d22","tid":1031823,"uid":141487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2066ff21ddc7a3396914a9f427a53eab054faa8","tid":1031823,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"讀完大學又會點? 只會起步再遲四年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:33:42.000Z","msg":"正解。搵下其他出路仲好，唔一定要靠讀書。加油！<br />\n<br />\n但千其唔好搵一d成世無得升嘅工，真係要做住先的話ok，但唔好長做"},{"pid":"89a74036982b99ff897154eae96562a3a9e6a6c5","tid":1031823,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:39:55.000Z","msg":"返工啦"},{"pid":"dd7e59ea9d12f6fb1a42c8535a5ce87a6e178758","tid":1031823,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"老老實實 ive 唔過2<br />\n不如去庇護工場打工算啦"}]}